name: Les Fretwell
descriptions: MP Les Fretwell is a cut non-player character still present in the game's files of Fallout: New Vegas.

A named NCR military policeman with some partially complete dialogue lines, located behind the NCR Embassy, but disabled. He is linked to the cut quest Jailhouse Rock, along with trooper Willis and two unnamed NCR troopers.
Les Fretwell was cut from Fallout: New Vegas.
